snippet.title: REFLEXIA Prototype ver. Trailer
snippet.description:
REFLEXIA is a visual novel that starts out as a parody of its genre and ends as a psychological drama.

You can try it for free here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1997680/REFLEXIA_Prototype_ver/
